  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe the cardiovascular risk profile in subjects who
      consume a marketed drinkable low fat fermented milk enriched with plant sterol.
      Investigations are lead prospectively and retrospectively among adults enrolled from general
      practitioners' database.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
